.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:262:## 5. REPORT CONTRACT
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-263-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:264:`benchmark-report.md` keeps this fixed ten-section structure. Do not merge, reorder, or omit sections.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-265-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-266-1. **HEADLINE / OVERVIEW**: one-line winner or status plus key metric.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-267-2. **AGGREGATE RESULTS**: one row per candidate, headline metrics, and verdict.
