.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-332-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-333-### Renamed or Renumbered Spec Packets
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-334-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:335:Do not rename the skill-local dated folder. Update the path in `source.md`, update cross-link tables in `benchmark-report.md` and `README.md`, and add a rename note in `source.md` with old slug, new slug, and date.
