.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md-1----
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md:2:title: "skill-benchmark: Lane C benchmark scripts"
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md:3:description: "Lane C scripts that benchmark a skill's real-world routing, discovery, efficiency, and usefulness — parse its playbook into gold, dispatch per scenario, score D1-D5, and render a dual report."
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md-4-trigger_phrases:
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md-5-  - "skill benchmark scripts"
