.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md:7:  - "Lane C D5 connectivity gate"
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md-8-  - "playbook scenario scoring"
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md-9----
.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/README.md-10-
