.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:79:- **Compiled child-process adapter**: runs the public front door with an isolated flag-on environment.
