codex
The benchmark flow is not a simple “run with the flag on” switch: Lane C currently produces an evaluator report from replay, probe, and optional live evidence, while its archived report has no compiled-route provenance. I’m tracing the orchestrator and renderer boundaries now, because frozen scorer constraints force the parity work outside those three files.
