    36	     folders on disk: one row per shipped run-label folder, one folder per row.
    37	     New run-label values must match ^[a-z0-9]+(?:-[a-z0-9]+)*$.
    38	  5. Validate:
    39	     python3 .opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/validate_document.py \
    40	       .opencode/skills/<hub>/benchmark/README.md
    41	     Iterate until 0 issues.
