.opencode/commands/deep/skill-benchmark.md-22-> 2. Run the Mandatory Input Gate (below) - resolve ALL inputs (in :confirm/no-suffix, present them and wait for confirmation; in :auto, resolve confidently or fail fast naming the missing inputs)
.opencode/commands/deep/skill-benchmark.md-23-> 3. Load the matching workflow YAML and execute it only after both gates pass
.opencode/commands/deep/skill-benchmark.md-24->
