.opencode/commands/deep/skill-benchmark.md-82-- **trace mode** — `router` (Mode A, deterministic, default/CI) or `live` (Mode B, BUILT — playbook corpus dispatched through `cli-opencode`).
.opencode/commands/deep/skill-benchmark.md-83-- **advisor mode** (optional) — `python` enables the opt-in D1-inter advisor probe; off by default and in CI.
