.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/SKILL.md-53-- **Lane A** — proposal-first loop for any bounded agent file: packet-local candidates, dynamic 5-dimension scoring, append-only evidence, guarded promotion/rollback with drift review kept separate. See §3.
