.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/references/skill-benchmark/operator-guide.md:42:`--advisor-mode=python` enables the **D1-inter** advisor probe — the deterministic in-repo SQLite advisor, scored out-of-band so the answer cannot leak. It is **off by default** (and in CI) to keep the pure-router path fast and dependency-free; enable it to lift a Mode A run from 4-dimension to 5-dimension coverage.
